01:15:28,396 --> 01:15:30,857
I mean, as Christians


1084
01:15:30,857 --> 01:15:31,958
let's not pretend.


1085
01:15:33,058 --> 01:15:36,019
We drive, we get angry, amen?


1086
01:15:36,019 --> 01:15:38,762
I mean, anger happens.


1087
01:15:38,762 --> 01:15:41,603
