1091
01:15:47,864 --> 01:15:49,224
You were overlooked.


1092
01:15:49,224 --> 01:15:50,925
Injustice happened to you.


1093
01:15:50,925 --> 01:15:53,545
There's real situations that happen in your life


1094
01:15:53,545 --> 01:15:54,926
and you were angry.


1095
01:15:54,926 --> 01:15:57,746
You were mad.


1096
01:15:57,746 --> 01:16:00,587
What do you do?


1097
01:16:00,587 --> 01:16:03,668
It says, be angry and what?


1098
01:16:03,668 --> 01:16:04,408
Sin not, but hear.


1099
01:16:05,693 --> 01:16:09,034
Let not the sun go down upon your wrath.


1100
01:16:09,034 --> 01:16:14,116
It tells me there should be a completion date to anger.


1101
01:16:15,537 --> 01:16:17,118
And that's the problem.


1102
01:16:17,118 --> 01:16:20,159
Some of us went to bed angry.


1103
01:16:20,159 --> 01:16:22,180
Don't let the sun go down upon your wrath.


1104
01:16:22,180 --> 01:16:25,121
But when we let the sun go down upon our wrath


1105
01:16:25,121 --> 01:16:26,021
what do we begin to do?


1106
01:16:26,021 --> 01:16:26,962
We begin to nurse it.


1107
01:16:28,302 --> 01:16:29,663
Man, we think it over in our mind.


1108
01:16:29,663 --> 01:16:31,664
I can't stand that person.


1109
01:16:31,664 --> 01:16:33,544
Why'd they do that to me?


1110
01:16:33,544 --> 01:16:35,897
I'll never go around that person again.


1111
01:16:35,897 --> 01:16:37,258
I'll never trust them again.


1112
01:16:37,258 --> 01:16:38,859
And we rehearse it.


1113
01:16:38,859 --> 01:16:40,239
And we rehearse it.


1114
01:16:40,239 --> 01:16:41,320
And we rehearse it.


1115
01:16:41,320 --> 01:16:42,721
So we go to bed angry.


1116
01:16:42,721 --> 01:16:46,223
And then the next verse says, neither give place to where?


1117
01:16:46,223 --> 01:16:48,084
To where?


1118
01:16:49,304 --> 01:16:54,367
So if you go to bed angry, scripturally speaking


1119
01:16:54,367 --> 01:16:56,508
you are giving place to who?


1120
01:16:57,669 --> 01:17:03,352
Now the word place means a spot, location, position, home, a room.


1121
01:17:05,069 --> 01:17:06,531
Think about that.


1122
01:17:06,531 --> 01:17:10,096
You are giving the enemy a room.


1123
01:17:10,096 --> 01:17:14,293
Inside, you are ceding ground to the enemy.


1124
01:17:14,293 --> 01:17:17,255
That violation that happened to you


1125
01:17:17,255 --> 01:17:19,377
that you don't know how to process


1126
01:17:19,377 --> 01:17:25,261
that you're trying to mop up your whole life, running everywhere to and fro looking for answers


1127
01:17:25,261 --> 01:17:28,103
and now that you've given the devil a place


1128
01:17:28,103 --> 01:17:30,044
and then I think of 2 Corinthians 10, 4


1129
01:17:30,044 --> 01:17:32,826
for the weapons of our warfare are not carnal,


1130
01:17:32,826 --> 01:17:37,550
but mighty through God to the pulling down of strongholds.


1131
01:17:39,151 --> 01:17:44,012
That's ground you've ceded to the enemy.


1132
01:17:44,012 --> 01:17:46,835
How did you cede ground to the enemy?


1133
01:17:46,835 --> 01:17:49,497
By going to bed, what?


1134
01:17:49,497 --> 01:17:50,618
Angry.


1135
01:17:50,618 --> 01:17:52,580
And you gave him a place.


1136
01:17:52,580 --> 01:17:55,222
And now he operates out of that place.


1137
01:17:55,222 --> 01:17:57,244
And all these things come from it.


1138
01:17:57,244 --> 01:18:03,870
Relationships, addiction, drug, promiscuity, and all these things.


1139
01:18:03,870 --> 01:18:06,452
And I'm saying this to you this morning


1140
01:18:06,452 --> 01:18:09,035
because as I talk to people every day


1141
01:18:09,035 --> 01:18:10,076
that's what I've seen.


1142
01:18:11,311 --> 01:18:12,592
There was a guy a number of years ago.


1143
01:18:12,592 --> 01:18:13,413
His name was Michael.


1144
01:18:13,413 --> 01:18:16,135
Incredibly talented pianist.


1145
01:18:16,135 --> 01:18:17,476
Classically trained.


1146
01:18:17,476 --> 01:18:18,837
Unbelievable.


1147
01:18:18,837 --> 01:18:21,018
But man, he could never get it right.


1148
01:18:21,018 --> 01:18:22,119
In the mission, out of the mission.


1149
01:18:22,119 --> 01:18:23,300
In the mission, out of the mission.


1150
01:18:23,300 --> 01:18:24,401
On drugs, off drugs.


1151
01:18:24,401 --> 01:18:25,041
On drugs, off drugs.


1152
01:18:25,041 --> 01:18:25,702
Same old thing.


1153
01:18:25,702 --> 01:18:29,764
And I finally asked him about his background and he said, well, what happened?


1154
01:18:29,764 --> 01:18:32,827
He was raised by his mother initially


1155
01:18:32,827 --> 01:18:35,388
and then his mother had a new boyfriend.


1156
01:18:35,388 --> 01:18:37,750
