1157
01:18:37,750 --> 01:18:38,551
It's either him or me.


1158
01:18:40,368 --> 01:18:42,512
And the mother chose the boyfriend.


1159
01:18:43,835 --> 01:18:46,299
And he said, now my auntie raised me.


1160
01:18:46,299 --> 01:18:48,703
And my auntie was kind of like a Cruella de Vil


1161
01:18:48,703 --> 01:18:51,099
and she was mean and overbearing.


1162
01:18:51,099 --> 01:18:53,040
She'd make me play the piano day and night.


1163
01:18:53,040 --> 01:18:54,020
I'd look out of the window


1164
01:18:54,020 --> 01:18:56,761
and see all the other kids playing football and basketball.


1165
01:18:56,761 --> 01:18:58,882
But I was never allowed to go with the other boys.


1166
01:18:58,882 --> 01:19:01,643
I was forced to sit into this room to play piano.


1167
01:19:01,643 --> 01:19:02,503
And now at the time


1168
01:19:02,503 --> 01:19:03,824
he was an older man.


1169
01:19:03,824 --> 01:19:07,225
He's still asking questions about his childhood.


1170
01:19:07,225 --> 01:19:12,907
Why in the world did my mother choose the boyfriend over me?


1171
01:19:12,907 --> 01:19:17,009
And you look at his life from outward, like a hippophile, a success.


1172
01:19:17,009 --> 01:19:18,009
What's wrong with you?


1173
01:19:18,009 --> 01:19:18,970
You're articulate.


1174
01:19:18,970 --> 01:19:19,610
You're smart.


1175
01:19:20,691 --> 01:19:21,812
You have a skill.


1176
01:19:21,812 --> 01:19:23,453
You're a great piano player.


1177
01:19:23,453 --> 01:19:25,335
Why can't you ever get it together?


1178
01:19:25,335 --> 01:19:29,579
You can mop it up by going to a drug treatment program, going to this program


1179
01:19:29,579 --> 01:19:31,460
talking to this counselor, doing this.


1180
01:19:31,460 --> 01:19:34,003
You need to get to the source.


1181
01:19:34,003 --> 01:19:38,587
And the source, I need to process what happened to me.


1182
01:19:38,587 --> 01:19:43,631
And I need, by the grace of God, learn how to forgive.


1183
01:19:43,631 --> 01:19:45,173
That's what happens there.


1184
01:19:51,631 --> 01:19:52,611
I think of Hebrews 12, 15.


1185
01:19:54,112 --> 01:19:57,653
The Bible says, looking diligently


1186
01:19:57,653 --> 01:20:03,696
lest any man fail of the grace of God, lest any root of bitterness spring up trouble you


1187
01:20:03,696 --> 01:20:07,397
thereby many are defiled.


1188
01:20:07,397 --> 01:20:08,938
Hallelujah.


1189
01:20:08,938 --> 01:20:10,299
Think about that.


1190
01:20:10,299 --> 01:20:12,640
Bitterness defiles people.


1191
01:20:12,640 --> 01:20:14,961
And so how does bitterness happen?


1192
01:20:14,961 --> 01:20:16,759
You go to bed angry.


1193
01:20:16,759 --> 01:20:18,540
They give the devil a place.


1194
01:20:18,540 --> 01:20:20,641
This place becomes a grudge.


1195
01:20:20,641 --> 01:20:23,062
This grudge becomes unforgiveness.


1196
01:20:23,062 --> 01:20:24,963
Unforgiveness becomes bitterness.


1197
01:20:24,963 --> 01:20:26,644
And now I'm bitter and I just hate everything.


1198
01:20:26,644 --> 01:20:28,465
Do you ever meet people that just hate everything?


1199
01:20:28,465 --> 01:20:31,106
Not nice people to hang around with.


1200
01:20:31,106 --> 01:20:31,646
That's no good.


1201
01:20:31,646 --> 01:20:32,126
That stinks.


1202
01:20:32,126 --> 01:20:32,967
It's too hot.


1203
01:20:32,967 --> 01:20:33,487
It's too cold.


1204
01:20:33,487 --> 01:20:34,628
It's no good.


1205
01:20:34,628 --> 01:20:35,428
And just bitter.


1206
01:20:35,428 --> 01:20:36,528
No matter what you talk about.


1207
01:20:36,528 --> 01:20:39,070
They're just bitter people.


1208
01:20:39,070 --> 01:20:41,691
And bitterness defiles you.


1209
01:20:41,691 --> 01:20:44,152
And that's where it has its source.


1210
01:20:44,152 --> 01:20:46,634
Somebody once says unforgiveness.


1211
01:20:46,634 --> 01:20:51,578
is like drinking poison and waiting for the other person to die.


1212
01:20:53,119 --> 01:20:54,100
Think about that.


1213
01:20:54,100 --> 01:20:59,524
Some of you can't stand somebody for what they've done to you


