01:20:59,524 --> 01:21:02,346
but they've moved on with their life.


1215
01:21:02,346 --> 01:21:08,751
And you are seated here dealing with the consequences of their filthy, vile actions.


1216
01:21:08,751 --> 01:21:10,712
And I want to tell you this morning


1217
01:21:10,712 --> 01:21:12,053
by the grace of God


1218
01:21:12,053 --> 01:21:15,928
it is time for you to move on.


1219
01:21:15,928 --> 01:21:18,869
They've already violated you once.


1220
01:21:18,869 --> 01:21:20,590
They shouldn't do it a second time.


1221
01:21:20,590 --> 01:21:26,732
Real quick, I asked some of our folks in our drug program before I came here last week


1222
01:21:26,732 --> 01:21:27,972
