01:21:42,002 --> 01:21:45,725
You need to get a happy space, a time out


1228
01:21:45,725 --> 01:21:46,685
go to the fun zone


1229
01:21:46,685 --> 01:21:47,886
whatever you want to do.


1230
01:21:47,886 --> 01:21:48,547
No.


1231
01:21:48,547 --> 01:21:50,428
The reason I'm miserable is


1232
01:21:51,989 --> 01:21:54,851
because of what somebody has done to me.


1233
01:21:55,872 --> 01:22:01,824
And they sit today in Chicago on a drug program trying to process the pain.


