1238
01:22:13,947 --> 01:22:17,827
And he says, it stole my joy for years.


1239
01:22:19,548 --> 01:22:24,249
Somebody else says, I still have a lot of work to do.


1240
01:22:24,249 --> 01:22:26,370
The emotions are powerful.


1241
01:22:26,370 --> 01:22:28,011
I need a lot of help.


