01:22:53,736 --> 01:22:59,101
Really give what we're struggling with the power to have mastery over us?


1252
01:23:00,482 --> 01:23:01,563
You know, so again


1253
01:23:01,563 --> 01:23:05,046
when we deal with this topic of forgiveness


