1280
01:23:58,719 --> 01:24:00,520
He doesn't run down and say, Kumbaya.


1281
01:24:00,520 --> 01:24:01,781
Hey, guys, all good now.


1282
01:24:01,781 --> 01:24:02,682
I'm second to Pharaoh.


1283
01:24:02,682 --> 01:24:04,143
Hey, look at my chariot.


1284
01:24:04,143 --> 01:24:06,766
Well, now he has go back.


1285
01:24:06,766 --> 01:24:08,047
It's Benjamin.


1286
01:24:08,047 --> 01:24:12,390
And he singles out Benjamin and he singles him out.


1287
01:24:12,390 --> 01:24:14,913
He recreates what happened to him.


1288
01:24:16,274 --> 01:24:17,935
My friend, as we're closing


