1313
01:25:33,893 --> 01:25:36,274
You've been in pain long enough.


1314
01:25:36,274 --> 01:25:38,455
You've rehearsed that long enough.


1315
01:25:38,455 --> 01:25:41,356
This morning you need to let it go.


1316
01:25:41,356 --> 01:25:43,217
Let's have every head bowed


1317
01:25:43,217 --> 01:25:45,537
